{"word":"G1288 - διασπάω - diaspáō - dee-as-pah'-o - Pluck asunder","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διασπάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diaspáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-as-pah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pluck asunder</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முறி, பீறு"},{"paragraph":"to rend asunder, to break asunder"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a>; to <i>draw apart</i>, that is, <i>sever</i> or <i>dismember:</i> - pluck asunder, pull in pieces.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}